parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of sudden braking or accidents, as the seat belt may not properly restrain the occupant.
symptoms: The seat belt retractor fails
causing injuries
the seat belt does not properly restrain the occupant
the seat belt becomes unbuckled from the seatbelt.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rear Seat Female Buckle Apparatus Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear seat female buckle apparatus can cause the seat belt to become non-functional, leading to injuries or fatalities in the event of sudden braking or accidents.
symptoms: The base plate of the buckle breaks off
allowing springs and other components of the assembly to fall out
the seat belt becomes non-functional.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the child safety feature can cause injuries or fatalities, as it may not properly restrain the child in a car seat, and may also cause inconvenience and discomfort to adult passengers.
symptoms: The child safety feature engages unnecessarily
locking the occupant to the seat
the seat belt must be undone to reset the safety feature
the feature is not comfortable for adult passengers.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rear Passenger Shoulder Belt Latch Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear passenger shoulder belt latch can cause the child safety seat to malfunction, leading to injuries or fatalities in the event of sudden braking or accidents.
symptoms: The rear passenger shoulder belt latch will not stay fastened while using a child safety seat
the child safety seat malfunctions
the child falls forward when brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling fan can cause debris to scatter, potentially injuring people in the vicinity, and lead to engine overheating, which can cause damage to the engine and surrounding components.
symptoms: Loud noise coming from under the hood
fragments of the engine cooling fan scattered under the hood
fan blade cracks or shatters
fan assembly failure
severe imbalance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning third sliding door can pose a safety risk, especially when the vehicle is in motion, as it may open unexpectedly, causing distractions, injuries, or accidents.
symptoms: The third sliding door does not close properly
requires holding shut and locking simultaneously to close
or opens unexpectedly while the vehicle is in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause multiple essential systems to malfunction, leading to a loss of comfort, convenience, and safety features, which can be distracting and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: All electrical items in the vehicle
including the radio
air conditioner
heater
and clock
become inoperative when the engine is turned on; the radio shorts out when turned on.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Gas Fumes Ingress through HVAC System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Gas fumes entering the cabin through the heater, air conditioner, and ventilation system can cause discomfort, nausea, and potentially lead to health issues for occupants.
symptoms: Gas fumes or strong odors emanating from the heater
air conditioner
and ventilation system
especially during hot weather conditions.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Windshield Wiper Failure in Cold Weather
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning windshield wipers can reduce visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during inclement weather conditions.
symptoms: Windshield wipers freezing or stopping during light snow or cold weather
reducing visibility while driving.
